title: PORT OF BROOKINGS HARBOR BOARD OF COMMISSIONERS MEETING
text:
PORT OF BROOKINGS HARBOR BOARD OF COMMISSIONERS MEETING ad date: 10/17/2015 
16011 Boat Basin Road, Harbor, OR 97415 Tuesday, October 20 , 2015 at 7:00 P.M. AGENDA 1. Call to Order and Roll Call 2. Approval of Agenda a. Regular Meeting-Tues. Sept. 15, 2015 4. Operational and Financial Review 5. Staff Reports 6. Agenda Related Public Comments-Limited to a maximum of two minutes per person. A "Public Comment Request", located near the entrance, must be completed and turned in to the Chairman prior to the beginning of the meeting. a. Connie Hunter - Green Building b. Ron Hedenskog - Health District Annexation d. Resolution 447: Board Duties and Responsibilities
